                <p><strong>Regeneration</strong> (e.g., <em>Planaria</em> and <em>Hydra</em>) is the ability to regrow a complete organism from a cut body part.</p>
                <div class="board-trap">
                    <strong>⚠️ Board Trap</strong>
                    Do not write that complex animals reproduce via regeneration. It is a specialized repair mechanism. Most organisms would not normally depend on being accidentally chopped into pieces to multiply! 
